DNA Analysis Project 

Description
This project analyzes DNA sequences using Python.

 Features
- Nucleotide frequency calculation
- GC content calculation
- Most frequent nucleotide detection
- Handles invalid characters

How to Run
1. Run the Python file
2. Enter a .txt file containing DNA sequence

Example
Input: ATGCATGC  
Output:
A: 2  
T: 2  
G: 2  
C: 2  
GC Content: 50%

